like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"中學生都識啦<br />\n樹大仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2359854d51608eb8221f61cccfaceaa010d8e1c","tid":872801,"uid":43650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d810f7937932aaf4f1c74c4b3c40d1484dc4fb","tid":872801,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"假設Quantity係Q，Total cost就係10Q。<br />\n<br />\n如果Q &gt;= Demand，Profit就係15 * Demand - 10Q。<br />\n相反如果Q &lt; Demand，Profit就係15Q - 5Q = 5Q。<br />\n<br />\n假設Q = 53<br />\n有20%機會係Q &gt;= Demand，有80%機會係Q &lt; Demand<br />\n所以expected profit = 0.2(15*53 - 10*53) + 0.8(5*53) = $265<br />\n<br />\n假設Q = 62<br />\nexpected profit = 0.2(15*53 - 10*62) + 0.05(15*62 - 10*62) + 0.75(5*62) = $283<br />\n<br />\n跟住用Excel一次過試哂53至125所有integer。<br />\n就搵到答案係Q = 82, Expected profit係$299.75"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ae41ffb4b8a4a2355543a2102b924e2d590687","tid":872801,"uid":43650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ea8edefadad0fea9c040ab15ef2558f7d751af0","tid":872801,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"中學生都識啦<br />\n樹大仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"咁我認我蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd07947bdec7ae55e0a0f17e63aa56a4fdfbe084","tid":872801,"uid":100661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"計期望值？<br />\n84份？"},{"pid":"3b305c7edf9143a14eb2925f169fbea346b6d9ef","tid":872801,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:25:54.00